    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "あーあー、やっぱりまたダメか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "*sigh* Nope‚ no good.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2533.333333333333,
          "startTime": 3.3333333333333335
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 4.533333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "今日はもしかしたらって\n思ってたんだけどな～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I thought maybe‚ just maybe‚\ntoday would be the day…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.07333334701649,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2566.6666666666665,
          "startTime": 7.1
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 8.26666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　麻奈\nどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm? Mana.\nWhat’s the matter?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 11.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna003.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてよ、琴乃ったら酷いんだよ\n今日もライブ来てくれないの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s Kotono. She’s so mean.\nShe didn’t come to the live today. Again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 17.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna004.m4a",
      "text": "今朝、私のマネージャーを紹介するからって\n言っておいたのに、「余計に嫌」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told her this morning that I would introduce my manager to her.\nGuess what she said? “That makes things even worse”!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.333333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 23.666666666666668
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna005.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんを芸能界に誘った悪い人となんか\n絶対会いたくないってメッセ来てたんだよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She just sent me a text‚ saying that she absolutely refuses to meet\nthe bad guy who lured her sister into showbiz.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.366666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "知らないところで悪人になってるな……っていうか\n誘ったのは麻奈だ。そこは、説明しておいてくれよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I guess I’m the villain now…But\nyou’re the one who invited me. You should’ve explained that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 37.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna006.m4a",
      "text": "そこは――まあ、その内に……ね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ er… I’m planning to do it when the time is right… okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "説明する気ないだろう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You aren’t planning to tell her‚ are you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 43.833333333333336
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna007.m4a",
      "text": "だって、それ言ったら、私だけが琴乃に\n嫌われちゃうもん。そんなの嫌だよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ if I told her‚ I’d be the only one\nshe’d be hating on. I don’t want that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna008.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとマネージャーは\n運命共同体でしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aren’t an idol and her manager supposed to be\njoined by a common destiny?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 54.6
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 55.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 57.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna009.m4a",
      "text": "ね？　ね？\nね～？？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right? Right?\nRiiight?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 59.53333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、分かったよ……はぁ。妹さんも\n一度でいいから、麻奈の歌を聴いてくれたらな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ fine‚ fine… *sigh* I do hope your sister\ncan hear you sing. Even just once.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そうすれば、きっと考えも変わると思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure it’ll open up her mind.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 73.03333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna010.m4a",
      "text": "絶対聴かないって言い張ってる。私がテレビに映ったら\nすぐチャンネル変えちゃうって、お母さん言ってたし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She refuses to listen. Mom told me\nshe would change the channel as soon as she saw me on TV.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈に似て、妹さんも頑固だな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That stubbornness is very much like you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 83.46666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna011.m4a",
      "text": "可愛いんだから、いつかは分かってもらいたい\nでも、そんなところも含めて私は琴乃が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s why I hope she’ll understand someday.\nBut I still love her very much—stubborn side and all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.46666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 89.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ今後も活動を続けていく以上、家族の応援は必要だ\n俺も妹さんが来てくれるような方法考えてみるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ support from family members is definitely important.\nI’ll think about ways to get your sister to come too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 98.76666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna012.m4a",
      "text": "本当？　ありがとう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Thanks!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "妹さんにいつまでも、悪人扱いされたくないからな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t want to be seen as the villain by your sister‚ after all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna013.m4a",
      "text": "あはは、そうだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. That’s true.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 108.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna014.m4a",
      "text": "ねえ、もし、琴乃に会って\n好かれたら彼女にしちゃう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ if you meet Kotono\nand she likes you‚ will you date her?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 113.13333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "はあ？　姉公認なのか？\nそもそも、会ったこともないのに分からないよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh? Have I got big sis’ approval?\nAnyway‚ I really can’t say without having met her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.86666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 120.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "う～ん……やっぱりダーメ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mmph… argh‚ no!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_01_03-mna015.m4a",
      "text": "私は認めないよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I will not approve!",
        "id": ""
      },
